  // - Url: Endpoint URL (required for HTTP transport)
  // - Command: Executable command (required for Stdio transport)
  // - Arguments: Command-line arguments (for Stdio transport)
  // - EnvironmentVariables: Environment variables to pass to the MCP server
  // - Enabled: Whether this server should be loaded (default: true)
